item_name: (READYSTOCK) 10L skincare mini fridge type mirror square minifridge kulkas skincare kosmetik makanan
item_desc:
Capacity: 10 Litre
Can be used for warmer and chiller
Dual plug: DC 12V for car and AC 100-240V or 60-70WATT for home
Temperature: heater 55-65C and freezer 10-25C
Types: Mirror Square
Mirror Square Size: 24.5 cm x 26.5 cm x 35 cm
Packaging Size: 40 cm x 29 cm x 32 cm
 
WHAT’S INCLUDED?
1x skincare minifridge
2x removable middle shelf
1x removable door shelf
1x home adapter
1x car adapter
A set of random stickers
 
HOME USE
Plug the 100C/AC wire into the appliance and connect the other end into your home outlet. Turn the temperature switch into either COLD or HOT
 
CAR USE
Plug the car adapter into the car cigarette lighter socket and the other end into the appliances 12V/DV socket. Turn the temperature switch into either COLD or HOT.
 
Our minifridge uses thermoelectric power circulating your choice of cold/hot air through a small electric fan. It delivers quiet and environmentally friendly cooling (no CFC Freon). Using much less energy compared to a traditional refrigerator.
